      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCARLET'S DESIRE (3) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (18.97) behind Jacobite Battle at this track. Must come into calculations. DANA MAC (8) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fifth by 4.5 lengths (19.23). Should be in this for a long way. PAW ULTRON (4) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished second (19.11) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Will give a great sight again. WHITE AND BLACK (7) comes into calculations after placing most recently.",
